{
  "stem": "26576.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "For us, the situation wasn't very bright because my father didn't get a job, and there was a lot that were called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They were-- this is a Russian word for people that were on the run, so they run away from Germany.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were-- we were also one of them, of course, and we-- we were thinking that what-- I mean, my father were hoping that he'll get a job.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "See that he couldn't get a job, he was a bit upset, but he was still hopeful.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I-- I remember he got sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You couldn't get medication.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We're completely no medication.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The situation with food was also not great.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I remember my father had a coat, which was called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "This is the type of coats that they have.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's a fur coat, a very warm coat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was a very bitter-- it was a bitter cold winter, and for everything, there was a queue.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know, the Russians brought already their system, and Lutsk was already very much so like the Russian system.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "For everything, he was standing in a queue, and I remember my brother and myself, the whole night, whoever was standing in the queue would get that coat.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And we would start like 6:00 in the evening and would stand until 9 o'clock in the morning, until the shops will open.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Sometimes, you would get some salt, which you could change later on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Sometimes, you would get-- and sometimes you would spend the whole night and get really nothing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I remember, we were standing, and then they were selling men's ties, which we-- we didn't need.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this was-- we were it Lutsk like this, sitting there, waiting for a job.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father got sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
